            <title><![CDATA[原中国铁路总公司党组书记盛光祖被查]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-03/ae21135333af4d6b93f92626937d66f2.png?VersionId=a1sqCiNWIt4Yu.F1vvI2JfkBkBy1KJdL&amp;itok=DFirq_HK" title="原中国铁路总公司党组书记、总经理盛光祖涉嫌严重违纪违法，目前正配合中共中央纪委国家监委纪律审查和监察调查。（互联网）" alt="原中国铁路总公司党组书记、总经理盛光祖涉嫌严重违纪违法，目前正配合中共中央纪委国家监委纪律审查和监察调查。（互联网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-03/ae21135333af4d6b93f92626937d66f2.png?VersionId=a1sqCiNWIt4Yu.F1vvI2JfkBkBy1KJdL&amp;itok=DFirq_HK" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
